	   <tr><td colspan=2>I wouldn't recommend specializing evocation.&nbsp;&nbsp;Many of our combat spells are conjuration based at higher levels.  Plus, nearly all of our non-combat spells are conjuration based with the exception of our pet buffs and such.  While it is possible to change your specialization later by doing a quest in the Temple of Solusek Ro, it is not something you really want to have to do.<br>&nbsp;<br>Krystala Mikasah<br>Magician (46) Veeshan<br><br>- The mighty oak tree was once a little nut that held its ground. -<br></td></tr>
