	   <tr><td colspan=2>The mage is my first ever character.&nbsp;&nbsp;I really picked a hard one, but I find it really interesting to play.  I spent my first 10 levels in Steamfront Mts.  Really good because certain parts of steamfront are for certain levels.  Especially if you are solo.  Later my friends ported me over in West Commons.  When I reached level 15, I went over to Crushbone for levels 15, 16, and 17.  Hint, if your a Gnome, do not kill Retlon, Bad Faction for us.  Since then I have been in the Estate of Unrest for 18 and still working on 19.  This is where grouping is a good idea because agro is high over there.  Plus the Estate of Unrest to me is really good experience.<br>&nbsp;<br>Decidido Ruedecita</td></tr>
