	   <tr><td colspan=2>The mage tower(<a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower" target=_new>http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower</a>) has several sections devoted to that very question. It's broken down into spell circles, IE: where to hunt 1-3, 4-7, 8-11... that sort of thing. As I've leveled, I've found that this is the resource I've used most often when deciding where to go. <br><br>Personally at low levels I just stuck around gfey, but I took a look at some of the other suggestions at the tower, and several suggested everfrost or misty thicket. Might be worth taking a peek at, for variety if nothing else.<br><br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, the Mad Mage of Povar, etc...<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
