	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, I have a perfect spot for you for those levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to Freerot and hunt in front of Cazic-Thule.  There are several lizard men in that area that are single pulls even though they appear to be close to each other.  You are looking for the pair by eastern bridge and a few more at the corners of the little pyramids.  The blue cons are Tae Ew Disciples, Defenders, Warders and Probationers.  Good XP, and because you are in a newbie zone, very little chance of getting jacked by a wandering mob.  I did three levels here very easily, quickly and safely in the 22-26 range.  Good luck.<br><br>Zithryn Sindar<br>41 Magician of Tunare<br>Quellious<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
