	   <tr><td colspan=2>By 49+, your mana regen is amazing by cannipetting and at 56 you get trods.<br><br>Cannipetting is casting a pet, and reclaiming him.&nbsp;&nbsp;At 49 earth and 50 MS2, you can gain back 6-11% mana per cycle, depending on whether you have spec'ed conjuration, have summoning efficiency gear, etc.  I can go from 0 mana to full up in 8 casts.  Using a trod charge at the end, I can summon a last pet, burnout him, DS him and still be full mana and ready to go.<br><br>However, at lower levels, I admit that we could use some mana regen.<br>&nbsp;<br>--<br>Jeroo Ashstaff</td></tr>
